cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image analysis and classification using deep convolutional networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of machine learning algorithms for this task also makes it likely to fall under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL) due to the use of deep learning techniques. Additionally, the use of neural networks for classification makes it likely to fall under the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
